org.jamplate.model

Interface Compilation

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CompilationImpl

    public interface Compilation
extends java.io.Serializable
    A compilation is a structure holding the variables for a single compilation unit (like a file).
    The implementing class must support serialization.
    Since:
    0.2.0 ~2021.04.28
    Version:
    0.2.0
    Author:
    LSafer
